    <item>
      <title>尽管电动汽车需求放缓，宁德时代全年收入仍大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/catl-full-year-income-jumps-even-as-electric-car-demand-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的电动汽车电池制造商宁德时代新能源科技有限公司(Contemporary Amperex Technology Co. Ltd.)公布的全年净利润超出预期，这家全球最大的电动汽车电池制造商成功击退了竞争对手，同时受益于投入成本的下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/catl-full-year-income-jumps-even-as-electric-car-demand-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 12:48:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约制造业指数合约超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/new-york-manufacturing-index-contracts-by-more-than-projected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于订单、发货和就业指标均下降，纽约州工厂活动 3 月份收缩幅度超过预期，而制造商对其转嫁成本的能力仍充满信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/new-york-manufacturing-index-contracts-by-more-than-projected</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>买家不敢碰的房屋揭示了智利的危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/chile-housing-crisis-apartments-remain-empty-as-buyers-stay-away</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利有如此多的公寓空置，政府正在考虑介入购买一些。在一个通常以住房短缺为问题的世界里，这是一个不寻常的举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/chile-housing-crisis-apartments-remain-empty-as-buyers-stay-away</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
