      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 10:36:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>兴登堡因涉嫌俄罗斯领带而卖空波兰零售商 LPP</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/poland-s-lpp-plunges-after-hindenburg-takes-short-position</link>
      <description><![CDATA[激进卖空者兴登堡研究公司 (Hindenburg Research) 表示，东欧最大时尚零售商之一从俄罗斯撤军是“骗局”，导致该公司股价暴跌 35%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/poland-s-lpp-plunges-after-hindenburg-takes-short-position</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 08:18:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IEA 将预测转向赤字，油价维持近四个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在国际能源署预测 2024 年供应短缺之后，油价维持在四个月高点附近——与之前的盈余预测相反——前提是OPEC+维持减产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 23:28:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
